&lt;p data-start=&quot;837&quot; data-end=&quot;1041&quot;&gt;From first touch to signed agreement, you’ll own the full sales cycle—partnering closely with teams across Solutions, Customer Success, Product, and Engineering to drive long-term value for our customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1043&quot; data-end=&quot;1204&quot;&gt;You’ll be selling to companies like Marc Jacobs, Walmart’s Home Brands, TaylorMade Golf, and Citizen Watches. It’s a big responsibility—and a bigger opportunity.&lt;/p&gt;
