&lt;p&gt;Klaviyo is the marketing automation platform powering the world&#39;s fastest-growing ecommerce brands. As a Commercial Sales Manager, you&#39;ll lead a team of Account Executives responsible for bringing net new merchants onto the Klaviyo platform — to win a generation of brands rethinking how they own their customer relationships.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll build a team that wins consistently, runs a disciplined sales process, and moves quickly in a high-velocity, high-transaction segment. This is a role for a leader who is equally comfortable in the weeds of a deal review and in front of a whiteboard designing a coaching plan.&lt;/p&gt;
