&lt;li&gt;Run structured weekly 1:1s and team meetings that reinforce priorities, sharpen skills, and sustain a high-performance culture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and execute individualized coaching plans to close performance gaps and accelerate development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with AEs on live deals — joining calls, supporting negotiations, and helping navigate internal approvals for complex or high-value opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead timely, honest performance conversations in accordance with Klaviyo policy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion career development: understand each rep&#39;s goals and create a visible path toward them&lt;/li&gt;
