&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monitoring &amp;amp; Incident Response&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor anti-abuse signals, logs, and alerts to identify likely abuse and separate it from normal behavior; recommend mitigations within established guardrails.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Investigate and address compliance and deliverability-impacting abuse events, engaging and escalating for timely response and mitigation.&lt;/li&gt;
