&lt;li&gt;Generate and review reporting related to threat alerts and user log behavior (e.g., unwanted mail rate, time to detection, response time).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
