&lt;p data-start=&quot;351&quot; data-end=&quot;781&quot;&gt;At Klaviyo, we empower creators to own their growth. Our platform is purpose-built for ecommerce, going far beyond email and SMS automation to deliver a powerful customer engagement engine. As an Account Executive on our NewCo ENTR (Entrepreneur) team, you’ll help fast-growing online stores unlock their potential—enabling them to scale faster, connect deeper with their customers, and own more of their revenue destiny.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;783&quot; data-end=&quot;982&quot;&gt;This is more than a sales role. It’s a chance to directly impact the success of the businesses we serve while advancing your own career at one of the fastest-growing SaaS companies in ecommerce tech.&lt;/p&gt;
